==German==
===Etymology===
From {{OHG.}} ''wurst''. Possibly related to ''[[wirren]]'' (from Indo-European root ''*wers-''), which would point to an original meaning of "mixture".
===Noun===
'''Wurst''' ''f'' (''pl'' '''Würste''')
# a [[sausage]]
===Adverb===
'''wurst'''
# [[anyway]], [[anyhow]]
#: ''Das ist mir '''wurst'''.'' - I don't care about it.
